# ── Baseline skill runtime state ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Skills install deps + caches into their own dir on first run. None of it
# should ever land in the repo. Patterns scoped to skills/ so a future
# user-installed-elsewhere skill can opt out by living outside this tree.
skills/*/.playwright-browsers/
skills/*/.browser-session.json
skills/*/.browser-sidecar.log
skills/*/.highlight-*.png
skills/*/.venv/
skills/*/__pycache__/
# MEMORY.md is per-user data (credentials, resolved IDs). Baseline skills
# must never ship one — see skills/skills/SKILL.md "MEMORY.md patterns".
skills/*/MEMORY.md

# ── Baseline job runtime state ───────────────────────────────────────────
tasks/*/MEMORY.md
